      "conditions": {
        "minCustomerCount": 2,
        "maxCustomerCount": 9
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（客流还算可以。这样的话应该能向龙姐交代了……吧。）",
      "conditions": {
        "minCustomerCount": 10,
        "maxCustomerCount": 29
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（客人增加了不少。也多亏了龙姐的介绍……得感谢她才行。）",
      "conditions": {
        "minCustomerCount": 30,
        "maxCustomerCount": 79
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（客人多得忙不过来……！不过营业额非常好。龙姐也会吃惊的吧。）",
      "conditions": {
        "minCustomerCount": 80
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（还欠着很多债……龙姐会怎么说呢……）",
      "conditions": {
        "maxDebtPaidRatio": 0.3
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
